        <!-- Slide 6: Cultural Significance -->
        <div class="slide">
            <h2>Cultural Significance</h2>
            <div class="slide-content">
                <p class="slide-text">Today, Sopa Paraguaya is considered the national dish of Paraguay. It holds special cultural significance:</p>
                <ul class="cultural-list">
                    <li>It's served at almost every important family gathering</li>
                    <li>It's a traditional accompaniment to asado (barbecued meat)</li>
                    <li>It represents Paraguayan identity and cultural heritage</li>
                    <li>It's a symbol of resourcefulness and creative problem-solving</li>
                    <li>The recipe is passed down through generations</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="slide-img-container">
